OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright day for many, but
OL,6,Fcloudier skies across the south will
OL,7,Fspread northwards during the day, with
OL,8,Fsome patchy rain developing over
OL,9,Fsouthern hills later. Mostly light
OL,10,Fwinds and feeling a little milder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FVariable amounts of cloud,
OL,13,Fwith further outbreaks of light and
OL,14,Fpatchy rain, particularly across the
OL,15,Fhills. Some clear spells developing
OL,16,Ftoo with some mist and fog patches
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
