OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FRemaining cloudy on Sunday
OL,6,Fwith outbreaks of light rain and
OL,7,Fdrizzle. These tending to transfer
OL,8,Fnorthwards during the afternoon. Some
OL,9,Fbrighter spells possible too. Near
OL,10,Fnormal temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Ffor most, staying largely dry with
OL,14,Foccasional showers. Mild in sunny
OL,15,Fbreaks. Turning wetter and windier
OL,16,Ffrom the west on Wednesday, with
OL,17,Fperiods of rain developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
